Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Those who agree, please raise your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:13.99,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,{\fscx106}With the voice of the majority, both the choir club and\Nthe drama club will have Koumura-sensei as their advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.42,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,and they are hereby officially\Ngranted permission to be active.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.96,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You finally did it, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:31.53,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Congratulations on getting\Nthe drama club reestablished. {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:35.01,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I made lots of food to celebrate the occasion. {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:39.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. This is all thanks to your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:42.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I did a lot, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:48.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was the one playing the basketball match\Nas well as the one helping with Tomoyo's election!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:55.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for everyone here,\NI don't think I could have done anything. {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There are no words to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We can't relax now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The School Festival is coming up\Nbefore the summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:05.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Our goal is to take part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will we still make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:12.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wasn't this your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Now that it's right in front of you,\Nthere's no time to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:22.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to get excited\Nand reach out for it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.07,Default,All,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will work for it excitedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Visit my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.58,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'll go meet your father today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.94,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I want to discuss your future with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.29,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Of course I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.07,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,You were suspended the other day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.22,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Your father's at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes and no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He might be out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.56,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.58,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'll get my stuff together, so wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:40.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0\fscx30} {\r} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wanted to get advice from Koumura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I need to start practicing a lot starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:49.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:54.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're contradicting what you said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:01.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You told me to excitedly reach out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:05.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My hesitation disappeared with those words, and yet you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll talk about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you chasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.97,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okazaki Tomoya from 3-D. Okazaki Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.00,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Come to the faculty office immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have to drag me. I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I won't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can't trust my words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Without a moment of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since occasionally you're a liar…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:44.64,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 19
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:44.64,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}New Life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.72,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,This is an amusing scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.25,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okazaki being tamed by a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Usually, he's the one who takes care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.42,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okazaki has changed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.25,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Can you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.01,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Make sure Okazaki won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. If I can be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:13.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,D-Don't you have business with Koumura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ah right. That's important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Geez. Stop slacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:22.51,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,How do you tolerate his harsh language?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've become used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:30.51,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's just been your father around since you were little, right? {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.87,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,It must have been hard for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:37.46,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Think about raising a guy like you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.42,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,All right then. I guess I'll wait inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.90,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,That's how my job is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.36,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I'll wait until tomorrow morning if I must.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll… go look for Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.37,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Should I head over to Sunohara's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You ran away, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What happened to your practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:28.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Koumura-sensei wasn't there, so we broke for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I thought I would bring your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Make sure you follow me, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.11,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What is Tomoya-kun saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:48.00,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,No, I came today because I wanted to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:53.69,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I will talk with him personally, too, but today I wanted to hear what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:56.71,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Like I said, that's not something for me to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.10,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun is Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.10,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's something for him to decide himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:05.10,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,But he's still a student, so I must hear his guardian's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.46,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,No, Tomoya-kun is Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.89,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's not something I should meddle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:25.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In his mind, I'm no longer his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:31.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you before how I got in a fight with Pops, hurt my shoulder, and couldn't play basketball anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's been like that ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Despite living in the same house, we carry on with our lives separately. {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:44.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He has a gentle smile like that and has always lived alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pops and I haven't been family for a long time. {ep18}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Would you like to come over to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Only if… it isn't imposing on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:19.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think it'd be good if you maintained a little distance from each other and thought things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You two are a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:26.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,so once you're apart, I'm sure that\Neach of you will grow to miss the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:30.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then you'll remember how you loved each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:35.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,so that the next time you meet,\Nyou'll be able to sit and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, your father would…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's lived alone just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But you should visit your home once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The house I always returned home to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…but no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A place I may never return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:20.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or, maybe a day will come when I'll be able to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:26.01,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,Who knew you could have a dish with such freshness so deep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:29.06,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,And what's best is the personality of the owner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:33.89,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be happy enough that you came here simply to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.45,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.76,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,I plan to go with my family over summer—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.69,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To my friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You have a big bag there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll stay there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I haven't decided when I'm coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.16,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see. It'll be lonely here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:11.30,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Since you were good company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have issues, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.32,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What business do you have here this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Has Nagisa not told them about me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If you don't have any, then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You're in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Um, where's Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.97,San,San,0,0,0,,Welcome, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.79,San,San,0,0,0,,I look forward to spending the coming days with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Same here. Thank you for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hospitality? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:11.71,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san will be staying at our place for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.57,San,San,0,0,0,,You heard it from Nagisa a moment ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You knew…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But Sanae…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.07,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:28.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's really sad for a guy to lose his harem, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:34.02,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you don't have to worry about Akio-san, so please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:34.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You should at least look a little guilty, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.37,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Let's get back to work, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can use a room this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's usually a guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The futon is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you're not used to it,\NI can take it out and put it back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's fine. I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't leave it out all the time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're actually a pragmatist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have my hands full with my own stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:13.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But you're always worried about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Seconds, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.22,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey. Good bath, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.40,San,San,0,0,0,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's almost uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess I'll get used to it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you have to say it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:46.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.01,San,San,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're off, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I-I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Go and score!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Score with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:12.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was a little embarrassing, but both Sanae-san and the old man sent us out really naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's really fun to walk to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a little embarrassing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It is a little for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:29.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But thanks to you, I've gained a lot of confidence in many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:33.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll give it my best from today until the day of the School Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.30,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Costume prepares the costumes and props.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.94,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Sound plays music and sound effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:53.44,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Lighting lights the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.39,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's very, very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.70,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Looks like we need to distribute the roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:03.28,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You can do Sound, can't you?\NSince you played along with Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.53,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Looks like a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.33,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I was curious what happened to the drama club after the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.32,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's part of my job as Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:18.10,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,The workloads of Lighting and Sound depend on the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:24.27,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,A play with a fast tempo will involve a more complicated use of the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:28.05,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,The sound effects can be played with that keyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.16,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.95,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hair-raising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a great sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oh come on. Let me play with it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What was that, Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Instead of Okazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,you like me more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We shall live alone in a forest nobody ever enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The two of us, holding hands, will run through the forest wet from the dew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.03,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:04.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We turn around, and there's a furious Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And ahead of us were…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:11.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The murderous combination of Kyou and Tomoyo with fangs sharpened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,They didn't have to punch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But that skit was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:21.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:25.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said you had a play you wanted to perform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm not sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:41.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To summarize: You know the play you want to perform, but you don't know the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:54.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They are students of the Furukawa Cram School.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa Cram School?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.52,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,What? That's not our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.68,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Nat-chan is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.82,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone. Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.47,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:20.70,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I couldn't get a separate room ready in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You were the teacher of a cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:24.59,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:28.90,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Sensei. Please forget about that guy and start class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you mean, “that guy”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:36.51,San,San,0,0,0,,Everyone. You shouldn't speak like that to people older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.85,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're not busy with anything, help with the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,In fact, you should stand here and free me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We're most busy during mornings and evenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The bread I bake is pretty popular, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:57.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is Sanae-san all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:17:02.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Some kind-hearted people buy her bread once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about the bread. I mean the cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't it hard to deal with kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.77,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's Sanae's real job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She was once a teacher at a middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why did she quit being one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.11,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:40.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:56.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It just felt strange that you're staying at my house, so I couldn't help but visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not rare to have visitors at your place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You let Mei-chan stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:05.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, but you're a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, if I'm bothering you, I can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're not a bother at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's just… how do I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's strange to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Strange, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:27.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. By the time I was aware of things around me, my mother was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pops is… you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Seeing a family that gets along well gives me a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:41.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right. Dad and Mom take really good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:51.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yet, I have something I haven't apologized to them for that I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't say for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:05.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but when I was little, it felt like\NI did something really bad to Dad and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe you're just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Both Dad and Mom say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They always change the subject whenever I ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I can tell they are hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:21.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since Dad always softens at times like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:27.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's something hidden that I have to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Something you have to apologize for…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to know about it and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's how I've always felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:47.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I started talking when you didn't even ask about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:49.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing strange about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:57.38,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san! The bath is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I'll get in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm heading out to Sunohara's place a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've got to visit him once in a while,\Nor else he'll be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:16.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't come back too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Man, this room is so relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.03,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I told you, we don't serve that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You didn't bring a bento or something with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, since I already had dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:32.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let me guess. At Nagisa-chan's place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm so envious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you say, but it's kind of uncomfortable to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:45.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's great that they're letting me stay,\Nbut I can't get used to the homey atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're staying with Nagisa-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:50.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't get it wrong. I'm only having them let me stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's doing a favor for me since she found out that Pops and I don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:07.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What more do I need to know than that you guys are staying together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So basically her parents approve of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:12.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like I said, we're not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:16.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Unbelievable… You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What does it matter…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:39.28,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I'm collecting junk in an effort to make another doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.28,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Do you want a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:46.96,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Of course. It's lonely to be by yourself..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:48.28,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.78,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,She's not entirely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:56.78,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I only thought, if there were more beings like me,\Nthis place would become more lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.25,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.59,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Even if it might not work.
