Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:42.38,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No, I don't recall anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Ask Sanae about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:45.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:46.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:53.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're trying to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:57.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But, even if you do, don't tell Nagisa about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:58.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:00.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,‘Cause I said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:01.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:05.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn't go.
